## Homework

In your Microsoft Teams class you can find your first homework. The deadline is Sept 14, 09:00
Your second homework is on Github. You may upload your script to my Dropbox via this [link](https://www.dropbox.com/request/YBtWi4RK9X8fqMoTNCxV) and name it using the following pattern: SURNAME_NAME-HW_2.R. The deadline is Sept, 21, 09:00

